457
00:47:41,984 --> 00:47:44,945
You know, here on the outside...

458
00:47:45,613 --> 00:47:48,240
we do not have access
to some of the pleasures...

459
00:47:48,324 --> 00:47:51,243
that are so freely available on the inside.

460
00:47:55,664 --> 00:47:57,958
I have these.

461
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:06,092
- The gold ones are particularly bueno.
