462
00:48:07,301 --> 00:48:09,345
I just need a little encouragement.

463
00:48:12,264 --> 00:48:15,935
You have a very
sophisticated security system here.

464
00:48:16,060 --> 00:48:18,938
Claro.
We have all categories of cases here.

465
00:48:19,772 --> 00:48:22,566
What is Maria Gonzalez here for?

466
00:48:23,400 --> 00:48:25,569
You're investigating her case, n'est-ce pas?

467
00:48:25,653 --> 00:48:28,614
I'm investigating a fraud case.
She's a witness.

468
00:48:30,157 --> 00:48:32,118
She's had a finger-graft.

469
00:48:39,542 --> 00:48:41,460
Maria Gonzalez?

470
00:48:43,838 --> 00:48:45,131
Take a seat.

471
00:48:47,341 --> 00:48:49,510
- You okay?
- I'm good.

472
00:48:49,844 --> 00:48:53,055
If this is about my finger,
then I don't want to prosecute.

473
00:48:54,390 --> 00:48:57,309
This is not about your finger.

474
00:49:00,813 --> 00:49:03,232
I need to speak to Miss Gonzalez alone.

475
00:49:03,524 --> 00:49:05,526
You have no authorization.

476
00:49:07,528 --> 00:49:08,571
Okay.

477
00:49:15,411 --> 00:49:18,164
I'm investigating an incident
at your place of work.

478
00:49:18,289 --> 00:49:21,167
Fraudulent papeles
issued from your printer.

479
00:49:25,921 --> 00:49:28,841
In the last 14 days,
three people have died...

480
00:49:29,884 --> 00:49:32,636
while traveling from papeles...

481
00:49:32,720 --> 00:49:35,181
issued from your printer at the Sphinx.

482
00:49:37,516 --> 00:49:41,562
The people who come to us,
they're all doing something dangerous.

483
00:49:41,937 --> 00:49:45,566
You have to expect that, unfortunately,
some of them won't make it.

484
00:49:47,067 --> 00:49:48,694
One of them...

485
00:49:49,737 --> 00:49:54,033
