He was fond of bats. Remember him?

486
00:49:56,660 --> 00:49:57,620
No.

487
00:49:58,245 --> 00:50:00,247
Damian Alekan? You met him at a bar.

488
00:50:00,372 --> 00:50:03,167
You sold him a papel
which allowed him to go to Delhi.

489
00:50:03,250 --> 00:50:05,419
- When did he die?
- A week ago.

490
00:50:06,337 --> 00:50:08,047
I've been in here for 10 days.

491
00:50:08,130 --> 00:50:11,175
