788
01:25:18,488 --> 01:25:21,074
What does he remember about the crash?

789
01:25:21,241 --> 01:25:24,369
He knows he went to Shanghai.
He solved the case.

790
01:25:24,494 --> 01:25:26,913
On the way to the airport,
he crashed the hired car.

791
01:25:26,997 --> 01:25:30,375
As far as he's concerned,
he never went to Jebel Ali.

792
01:25:32,836 --> 01:25:35,756
- I'll leave you alone.
- Thank you.

793
01:25:43,555 --> 01:25:44,973
I've missed you.

794
01:25:46,141 --> 01:25:47,434
<i>Me, too.</i>

795
01:25:50,270 --> 01:25:51,730
It's good to see you.

796
01:25:55,859 --> 01:25:57,903
I've brought you some clothes.

797
01:26:01,573 --> 01:26:02,699
Daddy!

798
01:26:05,619 --> 01:26:07,329
Where have you been?

799
01:26:07,788 --> 01:26:09,831
Daddy did a silly thing.

800
01:26:10,207 --> 01:26:13,752
I crashed a car
but the doctors fixed him up real good.

801
01:26:19,007 --> 01:26:20,384
What am I thinking?

802
01:26:25,472 --> 01:26:26,431
I don't know.

803
01:26:27,057 --> 01:26:29,393
Boats. I'm thinking about boats.

804
01:26:31,478 --> 01:26:35,649
<i>Row, row, row your boat
gently down the stream</i>

805
01:26:37,234 --> 01:26:41,029
<i>Merrily, merrily, merrily, merrily,
life is but a dream</i>

806
01:26:58,338 --> 01:27:01,466
<i>I was exiled
because I tried to cheat the Sphinx.</i>

807
01:27:02,676 --> 01:27:04,636
<i>They left me my memories.</i>

808
01:27:05,470 --> 01:27:08,181
<i>They don't care what you think
